{"tid":1082422,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭長子林節思確認離開小米　9月赴德讀希臘哲學","createTime":"2019-03-29T02:54:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-01T02:11:39.000Z","uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"635612e05eafee86b3db8b49f310747e156e5e5f","tid":1082422,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T02:54:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2609940/org/cc9a04f3431d434b66cfe0a97dd538d9.jpg/Z9KLYd0cNHhGK2s9506VsObcXuoHtb3EdNmN8nTZjfI?v=w1600r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2609940%2Forg%2Fcc9a04f3431d434b66cfe0a97dd538d9.jpg%2FZ9KLYd0cNHhGK2s9506VsObcXuoHtb3EdNmN8nTZjfI%3Fv%3Dw1600r16_9&h=32da550f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早前有傳「香港第一家庭」有新動向，指特首林鄭月娥長子林節思（Jeremy）已經離開內地手機公司小米，這則消息終於得到證實。<br />\n<br />\n事源林鄭上周宴請前競選辦成員，Jeremy都在場，據悉他談及已經離開小米，並且已有新計劃，就是重返校園，9月負笈德國，選修希臘哲學的碩士。難道Jeremy都受爸爸林兆波薰陶，養成對希臘文化的興趣？<br />\n<br />\n林鄭上周宴請前競選辦成員，有幾十人出席，包括港區全國人大代表陳勇、全國政協委員陳清霞、東亞銀行副行政總裁李民斌、信和集團副主席黃永光、立法會前秘書長吳文華、西貢區議會主席吳仕福、金發局主席李律仁、見習騎師學校校長陳念慈、世聯顧問行政總裁麥黃小珍等，去年在禮賓府以主人家身份接待的「第一先生」林兆波，今次晚宴就不見其影，反倒兒子Jeremy是座上客，與前輩共聚晚宴。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，Jeremy席間談及已經離開小米，今年9月將會前往德國修讀碩士課程，選擇的科目是希臘哲學，未知這個決定是否受家人影響呢？事關林兆波去年亦說過在學習希臘文，至於媽媽林鄭，據悉都有叮囑Jeremy要多讀書。<br />\n<br />\nJeremy9月才會到德國上課，據知之前會先到其他地方旅遊一下。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85/311885/%E6%94%BF%E5%A3%87%E8%AB%B8%E4%BA%8B%E7%94%BA-%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E9%95%B7%E5%AD%90%E7%A2%BA%E8%AA%8D%E9%9B%A2%E9%96%8B%E5%B0%8F%E7%B1%B3-9%E6%9C%88%E8%B5%B4%E5%BE%B7%E8%AE%80%E5%B8%8C%E8%87%98%E5%93%B2%E5%AD%B8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%2583%2585%2F311885%2F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25A3%2587%25E8%25AB%25B8%25E4%25BA%258B%25E7%2594%25BA-%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E9%2595%25B7%25E5%25AD%2590%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25AA%258D%25E9%259B%25A2%25E9%2596%258B%25E5%25B0%258F%25E7%25B1%25B3-9%25E6%259C%2588%25E8%25B5%25B4%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E8%25AE%2580%25E5%25B8%258C%25E8%2587%2598%25E5%2593%25B2%25E5%25AD%25B8&d=88BycQanWGa6BXzVat85Hazbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=9896c008\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85/311885/%E6%94%BF%E5%A3%87%E8%AB%B8%E4%BA%8B%E7%94%BA-%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E9%95%B7%E5%AD%90%E7%A2%BA%E8%AA%8D%E9%9B%A2%E9%96%8B%E5%B0%8F%E7%B1%B3-9%E6%9C%88%E8%B5%B4%E5%BE%B7%E8%AE%80%E5%B8%8C%E8%87%98%E5%93%B2%E5%AD%B8</a>"},{"pid":"9c54ad421c93c0030e8197dd3010f45e19cbddcf","tid":1082422,"uid":184679,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T02:56:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hkpic.crntt.com/upload/201803/20/105015301.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkpic.crntt.com%2Fupload%2F201803%2F20%2F105015301.jpg&h=aaf785f2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5a53a8c1b7500a5ba976e3f329caa70dd8daa203","tid":1082422,"uid":11258,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T02:59:09.000Z","msg":"香港人：讀哲學 乞食咩"},{"pid":"10c5656c5e4315e6a984e82f5f4d7a23c1da8345","tid":1082422,"uid":184679,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T03:18:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://p.ananas.chaoxing.com/star3/733_434c/2f9fa8cd6f94a302534aaaeee52b71d5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fp.ananas.chaoxing.com%2Fstar3%2F733_434c%2F2f9fa8cd6f94a302534aaaeee52b71d5.png&h=8c26d97a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"86dcae69a27f2384e20587a4e0eecda2ea666449","tid":1082422,"uid":60281,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T03:23:47.000Z","msg":"離開中國既藉口"},{"pid":"b2f9ff880f4c09310028199f0d7b15d003a8e0b8","tid":1082422,"uid":166474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T03:25:14.000Z","msg":"唔番香港做特首辦助理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"a36b2a160bdb68536cc7f84bed54849083958d23","tid":1082422,"uid":147434,"like":33,"dislike":2,"score":31,"quote":{"pid":"635612e05eafee86b3db8b49